      "rationale": "Experimental validation was conducted using the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump test rig under controlled laboratory conditions matching the declared operating envelope. Flow rates (2.0–6.0 L/min) and rotational speeds (1500, 2500, 3500 RPM) were measured with calibrated instrumentation (flow: ±1.5%, speed: ±10 RPM). Temperature maintained at 37°C ± 0.5°C. Test conditions are documented in the experimental protocol and traceable to the operating envelope declared in the ContextOfUse. Achieved Level 2 meets the MRL 2 requirement."
